Subject: Wire desktop app icons to Nadia face assets

Use additive Nadia-specific icon assets supplied by overlay/ instead of
replacing upstream binary files. The icon source is the canonical Nadia face
portrait from the NadicodeAI repository, cropped and exported for the macOS
and Windows app bundle surfaces:
  - electron-builder bundle icon: assets/nadia-icon.{png,ico,icns}
  - Windows rcedit identity stamp: assets/nadia-icon.ico
  - runtime notification/window image lookup: public/nadia-apple-touch-icon.png
  - renderer favicon/onboarding logo: public/nadia-apple-touch-icon.png

